videos.description: Davion Mintz feeds Olivier Sarr, who powers his way to the rim for the two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Sarr's footwork leads to an easy dunk) 2020/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sarr's footwork leads to an easy dunk

videos.description: Just before time expires on the shot clock, Olivier Sarr coolly hits the fadeaway jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Sarr beats the shot clock with fadeaway jumper) 2020/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sarr beats the shot clock with fadeaway jumper

videos.description: Grant Golden bounces the pass between two Kentucky defenders to get Andre Gustavon an easy bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Golden threads the needle to Gustavon for the layup) 2020/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Golden threads the needle to Gustavon for the layup

videos.description: Richmond guard Jacob Gilyard picks off a Kentucky pass and hustles to save the ball from going out of bounds with a quick behind-the-back pass to Blake Francis.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gilyard's behind-the-back save leads to a Francis lay-in) 2020/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gilyard's behind-the-back save leads to a Francis lay-in

videos.description: Jacob Gilyard tosses inside to Nathan Cayo, who takes flight for the two-handed slam, plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cayo slams it down over two Kentucky defenders) 2020/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cayo slams it down over two Kentucky defenders

videos.description: Nathan Cayo and Blake Francis score 18 points each to lift Richmond over Kentucky, 76-64.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Richmond stuns No. 10 Kentucky behind Cayo and Francis) 2020/11/29 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Richmond stuns No. 10 Kentucky behind Cayo and Francis
